{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
[Csus2] Now I'm walking again[Am] to the beat of a drum.
[F] And I'm counting the steps to the door of your [E]heart.
[Csus2] Only shadows ahead, [Am] barely clearing the roof.
[F] Get to know the feelin' of liberation a[E]nd release.
{end_of_verse}


